11:41.466 --> 11:43.600 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Will it meet the
requirements of the Medicaid
program, the spending?

11:43.600 --> 11:46.500 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
LISA DESJARDINS: Think of the
