We're not satisfied.

12:08.900 --> 12:09.900 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
LISA DESJARDINS: Yes.

12:09.900 --> 12:11.933 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
That's right.

12:11.933 --> 12:14.033 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
