12:39.100 --> 12:43.233 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
When we talk about the
affordability of this,
the quality of the
coverage, how does this

12:43.233 --> 12:45.166 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
