the plans to be less generous.

13:04.733 --> 13:08.966 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Right now, the Affordable Care
Act, the sort of middle-level
plan that subsidy is based

13:08.966 --> 13:11.300 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
on, would cover 70
percent of the cost.

13:11.300 --> 13:14.166 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
