13:14.166 --> 13:15.900 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
So, would you have to pay more?

13:15.900 --> 13:20.233 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
An older, perhaps a
higher-income person,
might pay more for less.

13:20.233 --> 13:23.766 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And so that whole benefit of
what you're getting for your
money, that is going to be a big

13:23.766 --> 13:25.866 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
