be covered, mental health care,
prescription drugs, maternity

13:47.700 --> 13:48.966 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
care.

13:48.966 --> 13:51.000 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
