that didn't cover prescription

13:56.566 --> 13:58.200 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
drugs or mental health
care, what would that
mean for beneficiaries?

13:58.200 --> 14:00.233 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
There is concern there.

14:00.233 --> 14:02.833 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: All right,
