funding, specifically around
the cases of abortion.

14:06.633 --> 14:08.166 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
LISA DESJARDINS: That's right.

14:08.166 --> 14:10.100 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
