15:44.833 --> 15:46.266 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: All right.

15:46.266 --> 15:47.900 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Lisa Desjardins, Mary Agnes
Carey, thank you both.

15:47.900 --> 15:50.500 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
MARY AGNES CAREY: Thank you.

15:50.500 --> 15:53.800 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: There
