for every state in the country.

17:15.166 --> 17:17.433 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
And, Judy, as you know,
I'm a former governor.

17:17.433 --> 17:19.633 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
