17:19.633 --> 17:24.633 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Medicaid has been a 52-year-old
partnership for state and
federal governments to take

17:26.700 --> 17:29.766 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
care of the most needy
Americans, and then
was expanded in the
Affordable Care Act to

17:29.766 --> 17:33.866 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
