path that the House took.

17:48.200 --> 17:50.366 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Let me pick
up on the Medicaid point.

17:50.366 --> 17:55.366 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
