bill did make deep cuts,
changes in Medicaid.

17:56.833 --> 17:58.933 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
KATHLEEN SEBELIUS: Right.

17:58.933 --> 18:01.800 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: What Republican
senators say they are doing
is phasing this in, that they

