of these changes in Medicaid.

18:10.166 --> 18:14.433 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
So isn't this something
of an improvement, makes
it more acceptable?

18:14.433 --> 18:17.500 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
KATHLEEN SEBELIUS: Well,
delaying the awful doesn't
make it less awful.

18:17.500 --> 18:22.500 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
So I think having a few more
years of grace period is
probably a good thing, but they

18:24.633 --> 18:29.633 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
