been created by these changes.

19:32.800 --> 19:37.800 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
KATHLEEN SEBELIUS: Well, again,
I think it's important to
understand these populations

19:38.400 --> 19:40.500 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
don't disappear.

19:40.500 --> 19:44.233 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
So the federal government has
decided they will stop paying
for vulnerable people across

19:46.733 --> 19:51.733 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
