only have one insurer.

21:20.000 --> 21:24.066 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
These are fundamental problems
that had to be addressed one
way or another, aren't they?

21:24.066 --> 21:26.033 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
KATHLEEN SEBELIUS:
You're absolutely right.

21:26.033 --> 21:30.300 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
The coverage issues, getting
more insurers to offer coverage
across the country, needed

21:31.466 --> 21:33.500 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
to be solved.

21:33.500 --> 21:37.466 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And there are solutions for
that with the re-insurance
pools that have been proposed.

21:38.200 --> 21:40.266 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
