21:40.266 --> 21:45.266 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
And less means not
only premiums, because
about 85 percent of the
people get help with

21:46.366 --> 21:47.733 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
their premium coverage.

21:47.733 --> 21:49.366 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
But they want the pay
less out of pocket.

21:49.366 --> 21:52.500 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
Again, none of this
bill does that.

21:52.500 --> 21:55.633 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
In fact, it would shift
more cost on to individuals.

21:55.633 --> 21:59.800 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
So, fixing the Affordable
Care Act is important.

21:59.800 --> 22:04.800 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
The Trump administration, I
would suggest, has done nothing
but sabotage the act since

22:06.733 --> 22:10.866 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
they came to office, refusing
to enforce the mandate, refusing
to tell insurers they will

22:12.800 --> 22:17.200 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
pay the subsidies, which
has caused dropouts, and not
clarifying what the rules are.

22:18.366 --> 22:20.366 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
So, companies are indeed
charging higher rates.

22:20.366 --> 22:24.366 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: At the same
time, President Trump himself
has said he believes all people

22:24.366 --> 22:26.066 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
should be covered
by health insurance.

22:26.066 --> 22:30.733 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
He said again this week,
I want to see health
coverage that has heart.

22:30.733 --> 22:34.400 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
KATHLEEN SEBELIUS: Which would
be great, but that isn't what
is proposed in either the

22:34.400 --> 22:36.300 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
House bill or the Senate bill.

22:36.300 --> 22:39.700 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And both President Trump
has declared as great bills.

22:39.700 --> 22:41.266 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Well, I haven't -- I apologize.

22:41.266 --> 22:43.533 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
I haven't seen what he
said about the Senate bill.

22:43.533 --> 22:48.533 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
He applauded the House for
their terrific bill, which took
coverage away from 23 million

22:49.566 --> 22:51.600 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
Americans.

22:51.600 --> 22:54.366 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
We don't know how bad the Senate
bill is going to be, but I
can guarantee you millions of

22:54.366 --> 22:56.666 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
people will lose coverage
and pay higher costs.

22:56.666 --> 22:58.133 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: He
also called it mean.

22:58.133 --> 22:59.666 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
KATHLEEN SEBELIUS:
The House bill.

22:59.666 --> 23:00.666 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
The House bill.

23:00.666 --> 23:02.666 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: The House bill.

23:02.666 --> 23:06.733 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Whatever happens#~ here, it looks
