24:20.466 --> 24:22.833 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
He's the president
and CEO of PhRMA.

24:22.833 --> 24:25.866 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
It's the drug industry's
largest trade group.

24:25.866 --> 24:30.000 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
He will have a different
