24:34.633 --> 24:37.666 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
promoting health through
good food -- Hari.

24:37.666 --> 24:39.666 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Thanks, Judy.

24:39.666 --> 24:44.466 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Now to the crisis in Venezuela,
which takes many forms,
economic, political, social, but

24:46.266 --> 24:50.166 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
perhaps nothing is more
harmful day to day than
shortages of medicine and food.

24:51.533 --> 24:53.166 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Put simply, many Venezuelans
are starving to death.

24:53.166 --> 24:56.866 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And their government often can't
or won't do anything to help.

24:56.866 --> 25:00.700 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
